93.
256Araṇaṃ parittaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasaraṇo naparitto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ.

258Araṇaṃ appamāṇaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nasaraṇo naappamāṇo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ.
